AND OTHER

PROVIDES PROTECTION AGAINST LOSSES TO

DWELLINGS AND CONTENTS FROM A WIDE VARIETY OF PERILS, AS WELL AS COVERAGE FOR LIABILITY ARISING FROM OWNERSHIP OR OCCUPANCY. THE COMPANY WRITES

