ALL AMOUNTS IN THE TABLE REPRESENT SHARES REPURCHASED TO COVER PAYROLL WITHHOLDING TAXES IN CONNECTION

WITH THE VESTING OF RESTRICTED STOCK AWARDS AND EXERCISES OF STOCK OPTIONS, AND SHARES USED TO COVER THE EXERCISE PRICE OF CERTAIN STOCK OPTIONS THAT WERE EXERCISED.

