THE COMPANY ALSO HAS A VARIABLE INTEREST IN CAMPERDOWN UK LIMITED, WHICH SPC SOLD IN DECEMBER 2003. THE COMPANYS VARIABLE INTEREST RESULTS FROM AN AGREEMENT TO INDEMNIFY THE

