AFTER THE DATE OF AWARD. ANY OF THE DEFERRED STOCK AWARDS MAY ACCUMULATE UNTIL DISTRIBUTION AT A FUTURE DATE OR UPON TERMINATION OF A DIRECTORS SERVICE. THE SHARES OF THE COMPANYS COMMON STOCK ISSUED UNDER THE 2004 DIRECTOR COMPENSATION

