IN ADDITION, THE ST.

PAUL TRAVELERS DEFERRED COMPENSATION PLAN FOR NON-EMPLOYEE DIRECTORS AND LEGACY SPC AND TPC DIRECTORS PLANS ALLOW DEFERRED RECEIPT OF SHARES OF COMMON STOCK (DEFERRED STOCK) TO A FUTURE DISTRIBUTION DATE OR UPON TERMINATION OF A

