THE TOTAL AMOUNT OF SECURITIES

AUTHORIZED PURSUANT TO ANY INSTRUMENT DEFINING RIGHTS OF HOLDERS OF LONG-TERM DEBT OF THE COMPANY DOES NOT EXCEED 10% OF THE TOTAL ASSETS OF THE COMPANY AND ITS CONSOLIDATED SUBSIDIARIES. THEREFORE, THE COMPANY IS NOT FILING ANY INSTRUMENTS

EVIDENCING LONG-TERM DEBT. HOWEVER, THE COMPANY WILL FURNISH COPIES OF ANY SUCH INSTRUMENT TO THE SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION UPON REQUEST.

COPIES OF ANY OF THE EXHIBITS REFERRED TO ABOVE WILL BE FURNISHED TO SECURITY HOLDERS WHO MAKE WRITTEN REQUEST THEREFOR TO THE ST. PAUL TRAVELERS COMPANIES, INC., 385

WASHINGTON STREET, SAINT PAUL, MN, 55102, ATTENTION: CORPORATE SECRETARY.

